# ignore everything by default, opt back in
**

# What we actually need in the build context
!pyproject.toml
!uv.lock
!app/**
!README.md

# Re-exclude noise that might slip in
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.coverage
**/htmlcov
**/.venv
.env
.env.*
**/local-images
